                        <interp inst="t18550917-name-324" type="given" value="MICHAEL"></interp>MICHAEL BEST</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined</hi>. He pretended to be intoxicated, but he was not so much as he pretended.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
